    {
        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"search\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f50d\" role=\"img\" title=\"search\">:search:</span> <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Topology/Order/Basic.html#nhds_order_unbounded\">nhds_order_unbounded</a>, <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Topology/Order/Basic.html#mem_nhds_iff_exists_Ioo_subset\">mem_nhds_iff_exists_Ioo_subset</a>, and <a href=\"https://loogle.lean-lang.org/?q=Set.Ioo%2C%20Exists%2C%20nhds\">17 more</a></p>",
